    <title>【Python】批量移动同类型文件到其他文件夹的办公技巧</title>
    <link href="http://itliming2000.github.io/2022/02/27/%E3%80%90Python%E3%80%91%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%90%8C%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%B0%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/"/>
    <id>http://itliming2000.github.io/2022/02/27/%E3%80%90Python%E3%80%91%E6%89%B9%E9%87%8F%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E5%90%8C%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%88%B0%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%A4%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9E%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7/</id>
    <published>2022-02-27T15:45:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2022-03-07T04:17:05.213Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Python具有简单易学的特点，是当前最受欢迎的编程语言，其中最重要的原因之一，就是它能够利用多种多样的第三方的包，满足人们的多方面需求，今天要介绍的就是它在办公自动化的妙用。<strong>批量移动同类型文件到其他文件夹</strong><span id="more"></span></p><h1 id="一、代码"><a href="#一、代码" class="headerlink" title="一、代码"></a>一、代码</h1><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 批量搜索指定类型的文件，并将其移动至一新目录</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 导入相关包</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> os <span class="keyword">import</span> sys,path,listdir</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> shutil </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义搜索文件方法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">moveFileToDest</span>(<span class="params">root,target,dest</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    fileList = []       <span class="comment"># 创建fileList数组</span></span><br><span class="line">    items=listdir(root)     <span class="comment"># items 目录或文件的数组</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> item <span class="keyword">in</span> items:      <span class="comment"># 遍历数组items</span></span><br><span class="line">        filepath = path.join(root,item)     <span class="comment"># filepath --&gt;从root开始的目录或文件的 相对路径</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> path.isdir(filepath):        <span class="comment"># path.isdir(filepath) --&gt; filepath是否为目录</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">list</span> = moveFileToDest(filepath,target,dest)      <span class="comment"># 递归</span></span><br><span class="line">            fileList = fileList + <span class="built_in">list</span>      <span class="comment"># 补充输出的数组</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">elif</span> path.isfile(filepath):     <span class="comment"># path.isfile(filepath) --&gt; filepath是否为文件</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> filepath.split(<span class="string">&#x27;.&#x27;</span>)[-<span class="number">1</span>]==target:     <span class="comment"># filepath.split(&#x27;.&#x27;)[-1] --&gt; 截取filepath的字符串的最后一个.后的内容，即后缀名</span></span><br><span class="line">                shutil.move(filepath,dest)       <span class="comment"># 移动文件，从file到dest目录</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> fileList     <span class="comment"># # 返回结果为数组,满足递归</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义主方法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">main</span>(<span class="params">argv</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    path = argv[<span class="number">1</span>]      <span class="comment"># 要移动文件的目录</span></span><br><span class="line">    target = argv[<span class="number">2</span>]        <span class="comment">#目标文件的后缀名</span></span><br><span class="line">    dest = argv[<span class="number">3</span>]      <span class="comment"># 移动文件到的目录</span></span><br><span class="line">    moveFileToDest(path,target,dest)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__==<span class="string">&#x27;__main__&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    main(sys.argv)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="二、执行"><a href="#二、执行" class="headerlink" title="二、执行"></a>二、执行</h1><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">python move.py res sav dis</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如图，在 <strong>Anaconda Promot</strong>中执行，运行<strong>move.py</strong>将<strong>res</strong>目录下所有后缀名为<strong>sav</strong>的文件移动至<strong>dis</strong>目录中<br>（<strong>注</strong>：move.py与res目录，dis目录为同级）<br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/8b2338ade90f40d48e5b29ed24a64b6d.png"></p><h2 id="3-1-代码执行前"><a href="#3-1-代码执行前" class="headerlink" title="3.1 代码执行前"></a>3.1 代码执行前</h2><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/060347ac916840e1a602102d81e5fcec.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA56a75piOemg=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/6f0b328e08de439da15aa13edbd8d43e.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA56a75piOemg=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></p><h2 id="3-2-代码执行后"><a href="#3-2-代码执行后" class="headerlink" title="3.2 代码执行后"></a>3.2 代码执行后</h2><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/4661c6b7f29f4a878d115c454a5722fc.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBA56a75piOemg=,size_20,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16" alt="请添加图片描述"></p><h1 id="三、延伸"><a href="#三、延伸" class="headerlink" title="三、延伸"></a>三、延伸</h1><p>根据此方法，应还可以延伸出其他有关磁盘处理的工作技巧，比如批量修改文件名，给文件统一添加标具有特殊标识的字符串，可以使用filepath.split(‘xxx’)截取和path.join(abc,item)拼结的组合方式实现。</p><p>CSDN同步参考链接：<br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_48927364/article/details/123172853">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_48927364/article/details/123172853</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Python具有简单易学的特点，是当前最受欢迎的编程语言，其中最重要的原因之一，就是它能够利用多种多样的第三方的包，满足人们的多方面需求，今天要介绍的就是它在办公自动化的妙用。&lt;strong&gt;批量移动同类型文件到其他文件夹&lt;/strong&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
